///                                                 * esum[i] = (signed 20b)rsu[i] <cmp> (signed 20b)rsv[i] ? 20'h0 : 20'hFFFFF
///                                                 * Main operation is to replace sum[0] and sum[1].
///                                                 * Stage: sum
///                                                 ###
///               %unsigned 1  xdesInSelMode             
///                                    ###
///                                    * Operates in SIMD 4 mode; will be ignored in SIMD8 mode
