///                                    * vfmt mode 4KB page count of down sampled buffer stride
///                                    ###
///               %unsigned 10 422Line                   
///                                    ###
///                                    * vfmt mode 32-byte word count of 422 output line stride.
///                                    ###
///               %%        6          # Stuffing bits...
